MythNetvision
---------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALLATION:
---------------------------------------------------------------------

run (a Qt4 version of) qmake on mythnetvision.pro:

qmake-qt4 mythnetvision.pro

Type 'make' in the main directory to begin compiling

Once the make is completed, do a 'make install'.


CONFIGURATION/USAGE:
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Add the following to library.xml in defaultmenu:

    <button>
        <type>NET_VIDEO_SEARCH</type>
        <text>Search Internet Video</text>
        <description>Search popular video sites</description>
        <action>JUMP MythNetVision</action>
        <depends>mythnetvision</depends>
    </button>
        
    <button>
        <type>NET_VIDEO_TREE</type>
        <text>Browse Internet Video</text>
        <description>Browse highlights and entire sites</description>
        <action>JUMP MythNetTree</action>
        <depends>mythnetvision</depends>
    </button>

The items should now appear under Media Library.
